<li>
Demonstrated ability to effectively manage multiple and potentially conflicting priorities and workload in a mission critical operations support environment.</li>
<li>
Strong verbal and written communication skills with ability to work well in a team environment and customer focused.</li>
<li>
Proficient in managing load balancer, F5 preferred; VPN devices and VMware products.</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Additional skills:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Experience with Linux operating systems as a system designer, system programmer, or lead system administrator.</li>
<li>
Working knowledge of jumpstart, kickstart (Linux), SAN architecture, and LDAP implementations. Knowledge of CDE, Unix shells, shell scripts, Perl, and IP routing protocols. Knowledge of Intel based hardware system and components.</li>
<li>
Demonstrated leadership skills and being pro-active in process and products/services improvement.</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Required Skills/Experience:</strong></p>
