System design, system integration, and system administration functions in the Instrument Software Systems Section for heterogeneous computing environment with diversified customer base</li>
<li>
System OS and other third party software installation and upgrades, large storage array management, file system management and allocation, system security evaluation and implementation, user support and user problem resolution, system software and limited hardware troubleshooting, and lead other system support activities. -- -manage user accounts, file systems, and backups.</li>
<li>
Create and/or maintain system design documents and operational procedures.</li>
<li>
